N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 393.12 - State fund deemed party in interest

State Regulations

In any further consideration of the claim after payment has
been made into the aggregate trust fund, the State Fund shall be deemed a party
in interest. Notes
